sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,ModelStorage: Flow 1: InferenceService Model Serving Request
        participant Client as External Client
        participant Gateway as Istio Gateway /<br/>OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        participant VS as VirtualService /<br/>HTTPRoute<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
        participant AuthProxy as oauth-proxy /<br/>kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP
        participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant ModelStorage as Model Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        Gateway->>VS: Route via VirtualService/HTTPRoute<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (Istio mesh)
        VS->>AuthProxy: Forward to predictor service<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS
        AuthProxy->>Predictor: Authenticated request<br/>HTTP/8080, localhost
        Note over Predictor,ModelStorage: Init: storage-initializer downloads model
        Predictor->>ModelStorage: Load model artifacts (init)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Access Key / GCP / Azure
        ModelStorage-->>Predictor: Model artifacts
        Predictor-->>AuthProxy: Prediction response
        AuthProxy-->>VS: Response
        VS-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON prediction result<br/>HTTPS/443
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client2,DecodePod: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Request (Disaggregated P/D)
        participant Client2 as External Client
        participant GW2 as Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        participant Scheduler as InferencePool<br/>Scheduler<br/>gRPC TLS
        participant PrefillPod as Prefill Workload Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS
        participant DecodePod as Decode Workload Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS

        Client2->>GW2: POST inference request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        GW2->>Scheduler: Route via HTTPRoute<br/>gRPC, TLS
        Scheduler->>PrefillPod: Schedule prefill<br/>HTTPS/8000, TLS (self-signed)
        PrefillPod->>DecodePod: Route via routing sidecar<br/>HTTPS/8000, TLS (self-signed)
        DecodePod-->>GW2: Inference response<br/>HTTPS, TLS
        GW2-->>Client2: Response<br/>HTTPS/443
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over LMCacheCR,NodePV: Flow 3: LocalModel Cache Download
        participant LMCacheCR as LocalModelCache CR
        participant LMCtrl as localmodel-controller
        participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
        participant LMAgent as localmodelnode-agent
        participant DownloadJob as Download Job<br/>(storage-initializer)
        participant CloudStorage as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant NodePV as Node Local PV

        LMCacheCR->>LMCtrl: CRD Watch event
        LMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create PV/PVC<br/>HTTPS/6443, ServiceAccount Token
        LMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update LocalModelNode spec<br/>HTTPS/6443, ServiceAccount Token
        LMAgent->>K8sAPI: Watch LocalModelNode<br/>HTTPS/6443, ServiceAccount Token
        LMAgent->>K8sAPI: Create download Job<br/>HTTPS/6443, ServiceAccount Token
        DownloadJob->>CloudStorage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
        CloudStorage-->>DownloadJob: Model artifacts
        DownloadJob->>NodePV: Write to local filesystem
        LMAgent->>K8sAPI: Update LocalModelNode status
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over IGClient,ISvcB: Flow 4: InferenceGraph DAG Routing
        participant IGClient as External Client
        participant IGRouter as kserve-router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
        participant TokenReview as K8s TokenReview API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
        participant ISvcA as InferenceService A<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
        participant ISvcB as InferenceService B<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS

        IGClient->>IGRouter: POST inference request<br/>HTTP(S)/8080, TLS (optional)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        IGRouter->>TokenReview: Validate bearer token<br/>HTTPS/6443, ServiceAccount Token
        TokenReview-->>IGRouter: SubjectAccessReview result
        par DAG fan-out (splitter/ensemble/sequence)
            IGRouter->>ISvcA: Inference request<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (mesh)
            ISvcA-->>IGRouter: Partial result
            IGRouter->>ISvcB: Inference request<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (mesh)
            ISvcB-->>IGRouter: Partial result
        end
        IGRouter-->>IGClient: Combined response<br/>HTTP(S)/8080
    end
